4Geeks Academy offers a course on becoming an AI Machine Learning Engineer. The course is designed for beginners with no previous knowledge required. Students will learn to build their first ML models and start a career as a data scientist. The course duration is 16 weeks, with 3 classes per week. The class size is limited to 12 people. The course covers Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, and Statistics. Students will work with supervised and unsupervised learning models and explore algorithms like Close Neighbors and Decision Trees. The course also includes real-life case studies and the use of industry-standard tools. There are no prerequisites for the course, and it is available in both English and Spanish. Graduates receive a recognized certificate. For more information, visit the website: https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning. stop